thread.title_full: Skipper (formerly Jetaport) reviewed by Damian Garcia

author: Damian Garcia
title: Damian Garcia
text: I had a great experience with Sob McNeil and the Skipper service. I would have liked to move a little bit quicker, but the impression I got was that the timeliness was not as quick on the hotels part. Nonetheless, the job got done and I am pleased.
